    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s interesting how we don’t often use this principle when it comes to skills—even though we know it’s just as applicable. 10,000 words, after all, is all you need to be fluent. And ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "20 hours",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " is all you need to be useful.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
