      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "In many areas, knowing what slice of the figurative pie comprises the topmost percent isn’t so straightforward. But I think with rare exception, skillfulness is relatively easy to acquire.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
